*-----------------------------( General help )------------------------------*

   There are a lot help pages you can refer to but to avoid confusion you 
   should read the 'syntax' help page first.

   Usage to get help is: help <topic>
                    e.g. help syntax
	
   To get a list of topics sorted by the following aspect, try help for:
      background,   communication,    magic,      moving, 
      skills,       combat,           misc,       rules

   also you can list all topics with:
      help topics

